# Logging

- Use `Log` with appropriate tags.
- Redact sensitive data; avoid logging tokens or PII.

# Metrics & Diagnostics

- Add lightweight counters/timers as needed without third-party SDKs unless approved.
- Prompt user before transmitting diagnostics off-device.
